  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗科技系统的数据流图。核心组件是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，它有两个实例，一个叫Audit，另一个叫Code。它们都连接到LabAnalyzer，也就是Define节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Audit和Code都是DiagnosticEngine的实例，都指向Define。那HIPAA合规的数据存储怎么处理？需要单独画出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，加上HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，命名为Bail。EMR同步模块叫Barg，这两个要互相连接，而且Barg还要连回Bail，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Bail和Barg的双向连接已加上。Define到Barg的数据流也要画吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "要的，LabAnalyzer的分析结果要同步到EMR。另外还有一个SticEngine节点，叫Signal，它接收Risk节点的输入，然后输出到Barg。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "Risk",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Risk指向Signal，Signal指向Barg，这条链路完成了。Place和Press这两个节点您提到要放进来，但还没定连接关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Place是WChart的入口，Press是操作触发点，Place直接连到Press就行，表示用户从图表界面发起操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下整体结构：Audit和Code都连Define；Define连Barg；Barg和Bail双向；Risk连Signal连Barg；Place连Press。方向都是LR横向布局对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——Code到Define的连接方向确认一下，是Code指向Define，不是反向。另外Audit也是指向Define，确保诊断引擎的数据流向分析模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，Code→Define和Audit→Define都是单向箭头。Bail和Barg的双向箭头也保持。现在所有节点都连好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再检查一下：Barg连Bail、Bail也连Barg，这个双向没问题。但Define到Barg是单向的，只把分析结果推给EMR同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全理解。最终确认：九个节点，Audit/Code/Define/Barg/Bail/Risk/Signal/Place/Press，连接关系全部符合医疗数据流逻辑。可以定稿了。",
